The Fall Festival is spreading good-hearted tricks and tasty treats across Middle-earth.  Join in by starting at the Shire where Mr. Bilbo Baggins has left one last surprise for his neighbours....


<rgb=#FF0000>After accepting this quest, you can complete it to gain a map to the Party Tree in the Shire, where you can join the Festival. </rgb>
You can sniff burning leaves and candy apples, the fall festival has arrived!

The Fall Festival is in full swing! Join the hobbits in the Shire to begin your festivities.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>Completing this quest will grant you a map to the Party Tree, where you can join the festival. </rgb>
